sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Caller Service
    participant Ing as Ingestion Service
    participant Dedup as Idempotency Cache
    participant Pref as Preferences Store
    participant Q as Channel Queue<br/>(push/email/sms)
    participant Wk as Channel Worker
    participant Prov as Provider<br/>(APNs/FCM/SES/Twilio)
    participant St as Status Store

    C->>Ing: POST /notify {user, template, channels, idempotency_key}
    Ing->>Dedup: GET (user_id, key)
    alt duplicate
        Dedup-->>Ing: existing notif_id
        Ing-->>C: 200 {notif_id, status: queued}
    else new
        Dedup-->>Ing: miss
        Ing->>Pref: check user prefs (cached)
        Pref-->>Ing: enabled channels, quiet hours
        Ing->>Dedup: SET (user_id, key) TTL 24h
        Ing->>St: persist {notif_id, state: queued}
        loop each enabled channel
            Ing-)Q: enqueue {notif_id, payload}
        end
        Ing-->>C: 202 {notif_id, status: queued}
    end

    Note over Q,St: async delivery
    Wk->>Q: dequeue
    Q-->>Wk: notif_id, payload
    Wk->>Pref: re-check prefs (opt-out window)
    Wk->>Prov: send (rate-limited)
    alt accepted
        Prov-->>Wk: 200 ok
        Wk->>St: state = sent, attempts++
    else transient failure
        Prov-->>Wk: 5xx / throttled
        Wk->>Q: requeue with backoff (30s, 5m, 1h)
    else permanent failure
        Prov-->>Wk: 4xx
        Wk->>St: state = dlq
    end
